snippet.title: Survivorman VR: The Descent - Official Trailer | Upload VR Showcase 2023
snippet.description: Check out the trailer for Survivorman VR: The Descent, a survival game in which real-life survival expert Les Stroud helps you stay alive after a plane crash leaves you stranded on a freezing mountainside. Explore, craft, hunt, and survive soon on Meta Quest 2.
